      <h3>
       <span class="ss-icon ss-symbolicons-block">
        earth
       </span>
       Research News
      </h3>
      <p>
       <span style="font-family: ProximaNova-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: 1.25em;">
        Law students at the Abrams Environmental Law Clinic are working with Recovery on Water, a group of breast cancer patients and survivors who row as therapy, to improve water quality for the Chicago River.
       </span>
      </p>
      <p>
       <span style="font-family: ProximaNova-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: 1.25em;">
