     <div class="col4 quick_fact">
      <h3>
       <span class="ss-icon ss-symbolicons-block">
        cfl
       </span>
       Sustainability Plan
      </h3>
      <p>
       <span style="font-family: ProximaNova-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: 1.25em;">
        At the University of Chicago, we are seeking to place clear parameters and identify measurable results around what it means to be truly sustainable. The Sustainability Plan is organized around 9 areas and we approach each with aggressive focus, real metrics, and lots of enthusiasm.
       </span>
      </p>
      <p>
       <span style="font-family: ProximaNova-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: 1.25em;">
        Click
        <a href="https://news.uchicago.edu/article/2016/11/16/uchicago-takes-data-driven-approach-sustainability-measures-campus?utm_source=%2A+UChicago+News+-+All+Subscribers&amp;utm_campaign=6be0a1d2ad-EMAIL_CAMPAIGN_2016_11_16&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_term=0_4d15d79ba2-6be0a1d2ad-154150753">
         <u>
          here
         </u>
        </a>
        to learn more.
       </span>
      </p>
     </div>
